<li class="toclevel-2"><a href="#Islamic_view"><span class="tocnumber">3.3</span> <span class="toctext">Islamic view</span></a></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="toclevel-1"><a href="#Enforcement"><span class="tocnumber">4</span> <span class="toctext">Enforcement</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1"><a href="#Extensions"><span class="tocnumber">5</span> <span class="toctext">Extensions</span></a></li>
