<li><a href="http://www.sikhspectrum.com/052004/manbir_france_9.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.sikhspectrum.com/052004/manbir_france_9.htm" rel="nofollow">France: Religious Freedom in the Land of Voltaire</a></li>
