<li><a href="http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/europe/3474673.stm" class="external text" title="http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/europe/3474673.stm" rel="nofollow">French MPs back headscarf ban</a> (<a href="/wiki/BBC" title="BBC">BBC</a>, February 10, 2004)</li>
