ots">2005 Cronulla riots</a> •</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><strong class="selflink">French headscarf ban</strong> •</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/wiki/Imam_Rapito_affair" title="Imam Rapito affair">Imam Rapito affair</a> •</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/wiki/Knighthood_of_Salman_Rushdie" title="Knighthood of Salman Rushdie">Knighthood of Salman Rushdie</a> •</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/wiki/Pope_Benedict_XVI_Islam_controversy" title="Pope Benedict XVI Islam controversy">Pope Benedict XVI controversy</a> •</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/wiki/Lars_Vilks_Muhammad_drawings_controversy" title="Lars Vilks Muhammad drawings controversy">Lars Vilks Muhammad drawings</a> •</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/wiki/Fitna_(film)" title="Fitna (film)">Fitna (film)</a> •</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/wiki/Sudanese_teddy_bear_blasphemy_case" title="Sudanese teddy bear blasphemy case">Teddy bear case</a> •</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/wiki/The_Jewel_of_Medina" title="The Jewel of Medina">The Jewel of Medina</a></span></div>
